TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT TRUNC(C.ACTUAL_OUTAGE_END, 'MM') RFC_MONTH, SUM(CASE WHEN PFZ_COMPLETION_CODE_PROD ='Successful' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) RFC_SUCCESSFUL, SUM(CASE WHEN PFZ_COMPLETION_CODE_PROD ='Backed Out' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) RFC_BACKED_OUT, SUM(CASE WHEN PFZ_COMPLETION_CODE_PROD ='Failed' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) RFC_FAILED, COUNT(C.NUMBERPRGN) RFC_COUNT FROM ITSM_OWNER.SRC_SC_CM3RM1 C INNER JOIN ITSM_OWNER.ITSM_ASSIGNMENTM1_V A ON C.ASSIGN_DEPT = A.NAME AND A.PFZ_ORG='BTI' WHERE C.PFZ_COMPLETION_CODE_PROD IN ('Backed Out', 'Failed', 'Successful', 'Partially Successful') AND C.ACTUAL_OUTAGE_END >= ADD_MONTHS(TRUNC(SYSDATE, 'MM'), -12) GROUP BY TRUNC(C.ACTUAL_OUTAGE_END,'MM') /* SELECT TRUNC(L.STARTED_DATE,'MM') RFC_MONTH, SUM(CASE WHEN PFZ_COMPLETION_CODE_PROD ='Successful' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) RFC_SUCCESSFUL, SUM(CASE WHEN PFZ_COMPLETION_CODE_PROD ='Backed Out' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) RFC_BACKED_OUT, SUM(CASE WHEN PFZ_COMPLETION_CODE_PROD ='Failed' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) RFC_FAILED, COUNT(C.NUMBERPRGN) RFC_COUNT FROM ITSM_OWNER.SRC_SC_CM3PHASELOGM1 L INNER JOIN ITSM_OWNER.SRC_SC_CM3RM1 C ON L.NUMBERPRGN = C.NUMBERPRGN INNER JOIN ITSM_OWNER.ITSM_ASSIGNMENTM1_V A ON C.ASSIGN_DEPT = A.NAME WHERE A.PFZ_ORG='BTI' AND L.PHASE_NAME ='RFC PIR/A' AND C.PFZ_COMPLETION_CODE_PROD IN ('Backed Out', 'Failed', 'Successful', 'Partially Successful') AND L.STARTED_DATE >= ADD_MONTHS(TRUNC(SYSDATE, 'MM'), -12) GROUP BY TRUNC(L.STARTED_DATE,'MM') */

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT TRUNC(Q.SUBMIT_DATE,'MM') OPEN_MONTH, NVL(Q.PFZ_BUNDLE, 'OTHER') REQUEST_TEMPLATE, NVL(Q.PFZ_DIVISION, 'OTHER') PFZ_DIVISION, SUM(CASE WHEN Q.CLOSE_DATE IS NOT NULL AND NVL(REQUESTED_DATE, SUBMIT_DATE + 5) > CLOSE_DATE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) SLA_MISSED, SUM(CASE WHEN Q.CLOSE_DATE IS NOT NULL AND NVL(REQUESTED_DATE, SUBMIT_DATE + 5) <= CLOSE_DATE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) SLA_MADE, SUM(CASE WHEN Q.CLOSE_DATE IS NOT NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) SLA_TICKETS, ROUND(SUM(CASE WHEN Q.CLOSE_DATE IS NOT NULL AND (Q.CLOSE_DATE - Q.SUBMIT_DATE) > 0 THEN (Q.CLOSE_DATE - Q.SUBMIT_DATE) * 24 ELSE 0 END), 0) RESOLVE_HOURS, SUM(CASE WHEN Q.CLOSE_DATE IS NOT NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) RESOLVE_TICKETS, --EXCL WC ROUND(SUM(CASE WHEN Q.CLOSE_DATE IS NOT NULL AND (Q.CLOSE_DATE - Q.SUBMIT_DATE - NVL(CLCK.WAIT_DAYS, 0)) > 0 THEN (Q.CLOSE_DATE - Q.SUBMIT_DATE - NVL(CLCK.WAIT_DAYS, 0)) * 24 ELSE 0 END), 0) RESOLVE_HOURS_EXCL_WC FROM ITSM_OWNER.SRC_SC_OCMQM1 Q, ITSM_OWNER.ITSM_ASSIGNMENTM1_V A, (SELECT KEY_CHAR, SUM(TOTAL - TO_DATE('4000-01-01', 'YYYY-MM-DD')) WAIT_DAYS FROM SRC_SC_CLOCKSM1 C WHERE TYPE = 'ocmq' AND NAME = 'Pending Customer' GROUP BY KEY_CHAR) CLCK WHERE Q.ASSIGNED_DEPT = A.NAME AND Q.NUMBERPRGN = CLCK.KEY_CHAR (+) AND A.PFZ_ORG = 'BTI' AND Q.COMPLETION_CODE <> 'Cancelled' AND TRUNC(Q.SUBMIT_DATE) >= ADD_MONTHS(TRUNC(SYSDATE, 'MM'), -12) AND Q.CLOSE_DATE IS NOT NULL GROUP BY TRUNC(Q.SUBMIT_DATE,'MM'), NVL(Q.PFZ_BUNDLE, 'OTHER'), NVL(Q.PFZ_DIVISION, 'OTHER')

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT TRUNC(p.OPEN_TIME ,'MM') OPEN_DATE, a.pfz_service_tower SERVICE_TOWER, SUM(CASE WHEN sr.q1 IS NULL THEN 0 ELSE sr.q1 END) SURVEY_RESPONSE, SUM(CASE WHEN sr.q1 IN (4, 5) THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) SURVEY_COUNT_4_5, SUM(CASE WHEN sr.q1 IS NULL THEN 0 ELSE 1 END) SURVEY_COUNT_ALL from itsm_owner.itsm_probsummarym_v p, itsm_owner.itsm_assignmentm1_v a, itsm_owner.itsm_pfzsitesm1_v s, itsm_owner.itsm_countrym1_v c, itsm_owner.itsm_survey_results_v sr, itsm_owner.itsm_survey_invitations_v si where sr.numberprgn = p.numberprgn and sr.survey_invitation_id = si.survey_invitation_id (+) and p.assignment = a.name (+) and p.pfz_site_id = s.pfz_region_id (+) and p.country = c.name (+) and sr.survey_type_cd = 'INCIDENT' and p.status = 'closed' and sr.SURVEY_TYPE_CD ='INCIDENT' AND a.pfz_ORG ='BTI' AND TRUNC(p.OPEN_TIME) >= ADD_MONTHS(TRUNC(SYSDATE, 'MM'), -12) AND p.PRIORITY <> 'PROJECT' GROUP BY TRUNC(p.OPEN_TIME ,'MM'), a.pfz_service_tower

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT S.SNPSHT_DATE, GROUP_VALUE MANAGING_DIVISION, SUM(CIS_COMPELTE_REQUIRED_FIELDS) CRITICAL_DISCREP, SUM(CIS_COMPLETE_TOTAL_FIELDS) ONE_OR_MORE_DISCREP, SUM(CIS) SERVER_CIS FROM ITSM_OWNER.ITSM_CMDB_DISCREP_SNPSHT S WHERE GROUP_NAME = 'Managing Division' AND GROUP_VALUE IN ('WTI', 'WYETH') AND CI_TYPE = 'SERVER' AND CI_STATUS IN ('Build', 'Run', 'Run-Update') AND SNPSHT_DATE >= ADD_MONTHS(TRUNC(SYSDATE, 'MM'), -12) GROUP BY S.SNPSHT_DATE, GROUP_VALUE

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT TRUNC(C.ACTUAL_OUTAGE_END ,'MM') OPEN_MONTH, ROUND(SUM(CASE WHEN (C.ACTUAL_OUTAGE_END - C.REQUEST_DATE) > 0 THEN (C.ACTUAL_OUTAGE_END-C.REQUEST_DATE) * 24 ELSE 0 END), 0) CYCLE_TIME_HRS, COUNT(C.NUMBERPRGN) RFC_COUNT FROM SRC_SC_CM3RM1 C INNER JOIN SRC_SC_ASSIGNMENTM1 A ON C.ASSIGN_DEPT = A.NAME AND A.PFZ_ORG = 'BTI' WHERE TRUNC(C.ACTUAL_OUTAGE_END) >= ADD_MONTHS(TRUNC(SYSDATE, 'MM'), -12) AND C.PFZ_COMPLETION_CODE_PROD NOT IN ('Cancelled','Rejected','Not Attempted') AND C.PFZ_RETRO ='f' AND C.SUBCATEGORY <> 'PRE-APPROVED' GROUP BY TRUNC(C.ACTUAL_OUTAGE_END,'MM') /* SELECT TRUNC(L.STARTED_DATE ,'MM') OPEN_MONTH, ROUND(SUM(CASE WHEN (ACTUAL_OUTAGE_END - REQUEST_DATE) >0 THEN (ACTUAL_OUTAGE_END-REQUEST_DATE) * 24 ELSE 0 END), 0) CYCLE_TIME_HRS, COUNT(C.NUMBERPRGN) RFC_COUNT FROM SRC_SC_CM3PHASELOGM1 L INNER JOIN SRC_SC_CM3RM1 C ON L.NUMBERPRGN=C.NUMBERPRGN INNER JOIN SRC_SC_ASSIGNMENTM1 A ON C.ASSIGN_DEPT = A.NAME AND A.PFZ_ORG = 'BTI' WHERE PHASE_NAME ='RFC PIR/A' AND TRUNC(L.STARTED_DATE ) >= ADD_MONTHS(TRUNC(SYSDATE, 'MM'), -12) AND C.PFZ_COMPLETION_CODE_PROD NOT IN ('Cancelled','Rejected','Not Attempted') AND PFZ_RETRO ='f' AND SUBCATEGORY <> 'PRE-APPROVED' GROUP BY TRUNC(L.STARTED_DATE,'MM') */

TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT TRUNC(P.OPEN_TIME ,'MM') OPEN_MONTH, NVL(P.RESOLUTION_CODE, 'OTHER') INCIDENT_TYPE, COUNT(*) OPENED_TICKETS FROM ITSM_OWNER.SRC_SC_PROBSUMMARYM1 P WHERE TRUNC(P.OPEN_TIME) >= ADD_MONTHS(TRUNC(SYSDATE, 'MM'), -12) GROUP BY TRUNC(P.OPEN_TIME ,'MM'), NVL(P.RESOLUTION_CODE, 'OTHER')

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT TRUNC(i.OPEN_TIME ,'MM') OPEN_DATE, a.pm_service_desk SERVICE_DESK, SUM(CASE WHEN sr.q5 IS NULL THEN 0 ELSE Sr.q5 END) SURVEY_RESPONSE, SUM(CASE WHEN sr.q5 IN (4, 5) THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) SURVEY_COUNT_4_5, SUM(CASE WHEN sr.q5 IS NULL THEN 0 ELSE 1 END) SURVEY_COUNT_ALL from itsm_owner.itsm_incidentsm1_v i, itsm_owner.itsm_assignmentm1_v a, itsm_owner.itsm_pfzsitesm1_v s, itsm_owner.itsm_countrym1_v c, itsm_owner.itsm_survey_results_v sr, itsm_owner.itsm_survey_invitations_v si where sr.numberprgn = i.incident_id and sr.survey_invitation_id = si.survey_invitation_id (+) and i.pfz_orig_group = a.name (+) and i.pfz_site_id = s.pfz_region_id (+) and i.country = c.name (+) and sr.survey_type_cd = 'CALL' and i.open = 'Closed' and sr.SURVEY_TYPE_CD ='CALL' AND a.pfz_ORG ='BTI' AND a.pm_service_tower_grp = 'SERVICE DESK COMMAND CENTER' AND TRUNC(i.OPEN_TIME) >= ADD_MONTHS(TRUNC(SYSDATE, 'MM'), -12) AND i.CATEGORY <> 'service catalog' AND a.pm_service_desk NOT IN ('LOCAL', 'OTHER') GROUP BY TRUNC(i.OPEN_TIME ,'MM'), a.pm_service_desk

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT TRUNC(C.ACTUAL_OUTAGE_END,'MM') RFC_MONTH, NVL(A.PM_SERVICE_TOWER_GRP, 'OTHER'), COUNT(DISTINCT C.NUMBERPRGN) OUTAGES_COUNT FROM ITSM_OWNER.SRC_SC_CM3RM1 C INNER JOIN ITSM_OWNER.SRC_SC_SCRELATIONM1 RD ON C.NUMBERPRGN = RD.DEPEND INNER JOIN ITSM_OWNER.SRC_SC_PROBSUMMARYM1 P ON RD.SOURCE = P.NUMBERPRGN AND RD.SOURCE_FILENAME= 'problem' AND RD.DEPEND_FILENAME= 'cm3r' INNER JOIN ITSM_OWNER.ITSM_ASSIGNMENTM1_V A ON C.ASSIGN_DEPT = A.NAME AND A.PFZ_ORG = 'BTI' WHERE C.ACTUAL_OUTAGE_END >= ADD_MONTHS(TRUNC(SYSDATE, 'MM'), -12) AND P.OPEN_TIME > C.ACTUAL_OUTAGE_END AND P.CATEGORY NOT IN ('REQUEST', 'SERVICE REQUEST') AND P.PRIORITY IN ('HIGH', 'CRITICAL') GROUP BY TRUNC(C.ACTUAL_OUTAGE_END, 'MM'), NVL(A.PM_SERVICE_TOWER_GRP, 'OTHER') /* SELECT TRUNC(L.STARTED_DATE,'MM') RFC_MONTH, NVL(A.PFZ_SERVICE_TOWER, 'OTHER'), COUNT(DISTINCT L.NUMBERPRGN) OUTAGES_COUNT FROM SRC_SC_CM3PHASELOGM1 L INNER JOIN ITSM_OWNER.ITSM_ASSIGNMENTM1_V A ON L.OPEN_GROUP = A.NAME INNER JOIN SRC_SC_SCRELATIONM1 RD ON L.NUMBERPRGN = RD.DEPEND INNER JOIN SRC_SC_PROBSUMMARYM1 P ON RD.SOURCE = P.NUMBERPRGN WHERE PHASE_NAME = 'RFC PIR/A' AND A.PFZ_ORG = 'BTI' AND L.STARTED_DATE >= ADD_MONTHS(TRUNC(SYSDATE, 'MM'), -12) AND (RD.SOURCE_FILENAME= 'PROBLEM' AND RD.DEPEND_FILENAME= 'CM3R') AND P.OPEN_TIME > L.STARTED_DATE GROUP BY TRUNC(L.STARTED_DATE,'MM'), NVL(A.PFZ_SERVICE_TOWER, 'OTHER') */

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT TRUNC(P.OPEN_TIME,'MM') OPEN_MONTH, NVL(A.PFZ_SERVICE_TOWER, 'OTHER') SERVICE_TOWER, NVL(P.CATEGORY, 'OTHER') CATEGORY, COUNT(P.NUMBERPRGN) OPENED_TICKETS, SUM(CASE WHEN P.PFZ_REOPEN_COUNTER > 0 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) REOPENED_TICKETS, SUM(CASE WHEN P.PFZ_RESOLVE_SLA='MISSED' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END ) SLA_MISSED, SUM(CASE WHEN P.PFZ_RESOLVE_SLA='MADE' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END ) SLA_MADE, SUM(CASE WHEN P.PFZ_RESOLVE_SLA IN ('MISSED', 'MADE') THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) SLA_TICKETS, SUM(CASE WHEN (NVL(P.RESOLVE_TIME, NVL(P.CLOSE_TIME, SYSDATE)) - P.OPEN_TIME) > 5 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) OPEN_GT_5DAYS, ROUND(SUM(CASE WHEN (NVL(P.RESOLVE_TIME, P.CLOSE_TIME) - P.OPEN_TIME) > 0 THEN (NVL(P.RESOLVE_TIME, P.CLOSE_TIME) - P.OPEN_TIME) ELSE 0 END) * 24, 0) RESOLVE_HOURS, SUM(CASE WHEN NVL(P.RESOLVE_TIME, P.CLOSE_TIME) IS NULL THEN 0 ELSE 1 END) RESOLVED_TICKETS, ROUND(SUM(CASE WHEN (NVL(P.PFZ_RESTORE_SLA_TIME, P.CLOSE_TIME) - P.OPEN_TIME) > 0 THEN (NVL(P.PFZ_RESTORE_SLA_TIME, P.CLOSE_TIME) - P.OPEN_TIME) ELSE 0 END) * 24, 0) RESTORE_HOURS, SUM(CASE WHEN NVL(P.PFZ_RESTORE_SLA_TIME, P.CLOSE_TIME) IS NULL THEN 0 ELSE 1 END) RESTORED_TICKETS, --EXCLUDE WC SUM(CASE WHEN (NVL(P.RESOLVE_TIME, NVL(P.CLOSE_TIME, SYSDATE)) - P.OPEN_TIME - NVL((SELECT SUM(TOTAL - TO_DATE('4000-01-01', 'YYYY-MM-DD')) WAIT_DAYS FROM SRC_SC_CLOCKSM1 C WHERE TYPE = 'problem' AND KEY_CHAR = P.NUMBERPRGN AND NAME = 'Pending Customer'), 0)) > 5 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) OPEN_GT_5DAYS_EXCL_WC2, ROUND(SUM(CASE WHEN (NVL(P.RESOLVE_TIME, P.CLOSE_TIME) - P.OPEN_TIME - NVL((SELECT SUM(TOTAL - TO_DATE('4000-01-01', 'YYYY-MM-DD')) WAIT_DAYS FROM SRC_SC_CLOCKSM1 C WHERE TYPE = 'problem' AND KEY_CHAR = P.NUMBERPRGN AND NAME = 'Pending Customer'), 0)) > 0 THEN (NVL(P.RESOLVE_TIME, P.CLOSE_TIME) - P.OPEN_TIME - NVL((SELECT SUM(TOTAL - TO_DATE('4000-01-01', 'YYYY-MM-DD')) WAIT_DAYS FROM SRC_SC_CLOCKSM1 C WHERE TYPE = 'problem' AND KEY_CHAR = P.NUMBERPRGN AND NAME = 'Pending Customer'), 0)) ELSE 0 END) * 24, 0) RESOLVE_HOURS_EXCL_WC, ROUND(SUM(CASE WHEN (NVL(P.PFZ_RESTORE_SLA_TIME, P.CLOSE_TIME) - P.OPEN_TIME - NVL((SELECT SUM(TOTAL - TO_DATE('4000-01-01', 'YYYY-MM-DD')) WAIT_DAYS FROM SRC_SC_CLOCKSM1 C WHERE TYPE = 'problem' AND KEY_CHAR = P.NUMBERPRGN AND NAME = 'Pending Customer'), 0)) > 0 THEN (NVL(P.RESOLVE_TIME, P.CLOSE_TIME) - P.OPEN_TIME - NVL((SELECT SUM(TOTAL - TO_DATE('4000-01-01', 'YYYY-MM-DD')) WAIT_DAYS FROM SRC_SC_CLOCKSM1 C WHERE TYPE = 'problem' AND KEY_CHAR = P.NUMBERPRGN AND NAME = 'Pending Customer'), 0)) ELSE 0 END) * 24, 0) RESTORE_HOURS_EXCL_WC FROM ITSM_OWNER.ITSM_PROBSUMMARYM_V P INNER JOIN ITSM_OWNER.ITSM_ASSIGNMENTM1_V A ON P.ASSIGNMENT = A.NAME AND A.PFZ_ORG = 'BTI' WHERE TRUNC(P.OPEN_TIME) >= ADD_MONTHS(TRUNC(SYSDATE, 'MM'), -12) AND P.PRIORITY <> 'PROJECT' GROUP BY TRUNC(P.OPEN_TIME,'MM'), NVL(A.PFZ_SERVICE_TOWER, 'OTHER'), NVL(P.CATEGORY, 'OTHER')

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT TRUNC(Q.SUBMIT_DATE,'MM') OPEN_MONTH, NVL(A.PFZ_SERVICE_TOWER, 'OTHER') SERVICE_TOWER, COUNT(Q.NUMBERPRGN) OPENED_TICKETS, 0 REOPENED_TICKETS, SUM(CASE WHEN Q.CLOSE_DATE IS NOT NULL AND NVL(REQUESTED_DATE, SUBMIT_DATE + 5) > CLOSE_DATE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) SLA_MISSED, SUM(CASE WHEN Q.CLOSE_DATE IS NOT NULL AND NVL(REQUESTED_DATE, SUBMIT_DATE + 5) <= CLOSE_DATE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) SLA_MADE, SUM(CASE WHEN Q.CLOSE_DATE IS NOT NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) SLA_TICKETS, SUM(CASE WHEN NVL(Q.CLOSE_DATE, SYSDATE) - Q.SUBMIT_DATE > 5 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) OPEN_GT_5DAYS, ROUND(SUM(CASE WHEN Q.CLOSE_DATE IS NOT NULL AND (Q.CLOSE_DATE - Q.SUBMIT_DATE) > 0 THEN (Q.CLOSE_DATE - Q.SUBMIT_DATE) ELSE 0 END) * 24, 0) RESOLVE_HOURS, SUM(CASE WHEN Q.CLOSE_DATE IS NOT NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) RESOLVED_TICKETS, --EXCLUDE WC SUM(CASE WHEN (NVL(Q.CLOSE_DATE, SYSDATE) - Q.SUBMIT_DATE - NVL((SELECT SUM(TOTAL - TO_DATE('4000-01-01', 'YYYY-MM-DD')) WAIT_DAYS FROM SRC_SC_CLOCKSM1 C WHERE TYPE = 'ocmq' AND KEY_CHAR = Q.NUMBERPRGN AND NAME = 'Pending Customer'), 0)) > 5 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) OPEN_GT_5DAYS_EXCL_WC, ROUND(SUM(CASE WHEN Q.CLOSE_DATE IS NOT NULL AND (Q.CLOSE_DATE - Q.SUBMIT_DATE - NVL((SELECT SUM(TOTAL - TO_DATE('4000-01-01', 'YYYY-MM-DD')) WAIT_DAYS FROM SRC_SC_CLOCKSM1 C WHERE TYPE = 'ocmq' AND KEY_CHAR = Q.NUMBERPRGN AND NAME = 'Pending Customer'), 0)) > 0 THEN (Q.CLOSE_DATE - Q.SUBMIT_DATE - NVL((SELECT SUM(TOTAL - TO_DATE('4000-01-01', 'YYYY-MM-DD')) WAIT_DAYS FROM SRC_SC_CLOCKSM1 C WHERE TYPE = 'ocmq' AND KEY_CHAR = Q.NUMBERPRGN AND NAME = 'Pending Customer'), 0)) ELSE 0 END) * 24, 0) RESOLVE_HOURS_EXCL_WC FROM ITSM_OWNER.SRC_SC_OCMQM1 Q, ITSM_OWNER.ITSM_ASSIGNMENTM1_V A WHERE Q.ASSIGNED_DEPT = A.NAME AND A.PFZ_ORG = 'BTI' AND Q.COMPLETION_CODE <> 'Cancelled' AND TRUNC(Q.SUBMIT_DATE) >= ADD_MONTHS(TRUNC(SYSDATE, 'MM'), -12) GROUP BY TRUNC(Q.SUBMIT_DATE,'MM'), NVL(A.PFZ_SERVICE_TOWER, 'OTHER')

TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT TRUNC(I.OPEN_TIME,'MM') OPEN_MONTH, A.PM_SERVICE_DESK PM_SERVICE_DESK, SUM(CASE WHEN I.PFZ_CALL_SOURCE = 'PHONE' AND FIRST_CALL = 't' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) FCR_PHONE_INTERACTIONS, SUM(CASE WHEN I.PFZ_CALL_SOURCE = 'PHONE' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) PHONE_INTERACTIONS, SUM(CASE WHEN UPPER(I.PFZ_ACTION) ='RECURRING INCIDENT' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) REOPENED_INTERACTIONS, SUM(1) TOTAL_INTERACTIONS, ROUND(SUM(CASE WHEN I.PFZ_CALL_SOURCE = 'PHONE' AND NVL(PFZ_INTERACTION_STOP-PFZ_INTERACTION_START, 0) > 0 THEN PFZ_INTERACTION_STOP-PFZ_INTERACTION_START ELSE 0 END)*24*60, 0) HANDLE_TIME_MINS FROM ITSM_OWNER.ITSM_INCIDENTSM1_V I, ITSM_OWNER.ITSM_ASSIGNMENTM1_V A WHERE I.PFZ_ORIG_GROUP = A.NAME AND A.PFZ_ORG = 'BTI' AND A.PFZ_SERVICE_TOWER = 'SERVICE DESK COMMAND CENTER' AND NVL(A.PM_SERVICE_DESK, 'OTHER') NOT IN ('LOCAL', 'OTHER') AND TRUNC(I.OPEN_TIME) >= ADD_MONTHS(TRUNC(SYSDATE, 'MM'), -12) AND I.CATEGORY <> 'service catalog' AND I.PM_SELF_SERVICE = 'f' GROUP BY TRUNC(I.OPEN_TIME,'MM'), A.PM_SERVICE_DESK
